Volker Kauder , head of the
parliamentary group of German Chancellor  Angela Merkel ’s
 Christian Democrats , said the government’s main task is to
stabilize the euro and to strengthen  Europe ,  Frankfurter
Allgemeine Zeitung  reported, citing an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
